default&#xa0;
defaultPlanning requirements for cycle parking provision at residential/business developm
defaultents are enforced. For people to feel able to use their bikes, they need to be confident there will be a secure parking place at their destination to help prevent theft of their cycle. One quarter of those who have a cycle stolen give up cycling and don't 
defaultreplace their cycle.
